---
import Site from '../layouts/Site.astro';
import Waves from '../components/Waves.astro';
import { breadcrumb, jsonLdGraph } from '../lib/seo';

const repoUrl = 'https://github.com/decoded-cipher/nodrix';
const lastUpdated = 'June 5, 2026';
const site = Astro.site!;
const jsonLd = jsonLdGraph(
  breadcrumb(site, [
    { name: 'Home', path: '/' },
    { name: 'Terms of Use', path: '/terms/' },
  ]),
);
---

<Site
  title="Terms of Use | nodrix"
  description="The terms governing use of the nodrix software, which is open source under the MIT License and deployed to your own Cloudflare account."
>
  <Fragment slot="head">
    <script is:inline type="application/ld+json" set:html={jsonLd} />
  </Fragment>

  <section class="hero-glow relative overflow-hidden border-b border-neutral-200/70">
    <Waves />
    <div class="relative mx-auto max-w-3xl px-5 py-14 sm:px-6 sm:py-20">
      <span class="text-sm font-semibold text-accent-600">Legal</span>
      <h1 class="mt-2 text-4xl font-extrabold tracking-tight text-neutral-900 sm:text-5xl">Terms of Use</h1>
      <p class="mt-4 max-w-2xl text-base leading-relaxed text-neutral-600">
        The terms governing the nodrix software you deploy.
      </p>
      <p class="mt-3 text-sm text-neutral-500">Last updated: {lastUpdated}</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="bg-white">
    <div class="prose prose-neutral mx-auto max-w-3xl px-5 py-12 sm:px-6 sm:py-16">
      <p>
        These Terms of Use govern your use of the nodrix software. nodrix is open-source software that
        you deploy and operate in your own Cloudflare account.
      </p>

      <h2>1. The software and its license</h2>
      <p>
        nodrix is released under the <a href={`${repoUrl}/blob/master/LICENSE`} target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">MIT License</a>,
        which is the authoritative grant of rights to use, copy, modify, and distribute the software.
        The software is provided <strong>"as is", without warranty of any kind</strong>. To the
        maximum extent permitted by law, the authors and contributors are not liable for any claim,
        damages, or other liability arising from the software or its use.
      </p>

      <h2>2. Self-hosting and your responsibilities</h2>
      <p>
        nodrix runs in your own Cloudflare account. You are solely responsible for your deployment —
        including its configuration and security, the devices and data you connect to it, any
        Cloudflare usage costs it incurs, and your compliance with all laws and regulations that apply
        to you. The project does not operate or have access to your instance or its data.
      </p>

      <h2>3. Acceptable use</h2>
      <p>
        You agree to use nodrix lawfully, and not to use it to harm others or to infringe the rights
        of any third party. You are responsible for the content and conduct of the systems you build
        with it.
      </p>

      <h2>4. Third-party services</h2>
      <p>
        nodrix runs on Cloudflare and can connect to third-party services you configure, such as email
        or chat integrations. Your use of those services is governed by their own terms, and you are
        responsible for complying with them.
      </p>

      <h2>5. Trademarks</h2>
      <p>
        "nodrix" and the nodrix logo are marks of the project. Other names referenced on this website
        — such as Cloudflare, Blynk, ThingsBoard, Arduino, and Product Hunt — are the property of their
        respective owners and are used only for identification and comparison; their use does not imply
        affiliation or endorsement.
      </p>

      <h2>6. Changes to these terms</h2>
      <p>
        We may update these Terms of Use from time to time. Material changes will be reflected in the
        "Last updated" date shown above.
      </p>

      <h2>7. Contact</h2>
      <p>
        Questions about these terms? Contact us at
        <a href="mailto:hello@nodrix.live">hello@nodrix.live</a>.
      </p>

      <div class="not-prose mt-12 rounded-2xl border border-neutral-200 bg-neutral-50 p-6">
        <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-neutral-900">About this website</p>
        <p class="mt-2 text-sm leading-relaxed text-neutral-600">
          nodrix.live is our marketing website, provided for informational purposes and offered as is.
          Its content, including product comparisons, may change at any time.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Site>
